participant_b.entity_text: PHAC1 synthase gene from P. aeruginosa

verbose_text: Thus the main aim of the present study was to generate flax plants with over-expression of the PHAC1 synthase gene from P. aeruginosa and to characterize created plants in terms of their biochemical, mechanical and spectroscopic properties.
evidence: over-expression of the PHAC1 synthase gene from P. aeruginosa
